sequenceDiagram
    participant UI as Billing Console
    participant GW as ProjectBoardGateway
    participant Auth as SocketAuthService
    participant Users as UsersRepository
    participant Projects as ProjectsRepository
    participant RT as ProjectBoardRealtimeService

    UI->>GW: connect (Authorization, X-Tenant / auth.tenantId)
    GW->>Auth: validateAndGetUser
    Auth-->>GW: userInfo (reject API key)
    GW-->>UI: connection established

    UI->>GW: setProject { projectId }
    GW->>Users: findByIdForTenant(userId)
    GW->>Projects: findByIdOrThrow(projectId)
    GW->>GW: ensureProjectReadable(userInfo, project)
    GW->>GW: socket.join(project:projectId)
    GW-->>UI: setProjectSuccess { projectId }

    Note over UI,RT: Admin or system REST mutation (e.g. ticket update)
    RT->>GW: emitToProject(projectId, ticketUpsert, dto)
    GW-->>UI: ticketUpsert (room broadcast)

    UI->>GW: disconnect
    GW->>GW: socket.leave(project:projectId)
